but that\'s better than smaller. Easy to slip on and off and stay on feet.','I495361067'),(5,'2014-04-19',5,'Great buy','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Handbags & Wallets\', \'Cross-Body Bags\']]','I never bought anything from this brand before but I will certainly buy from them again. I love it, it\'s a great casual every day bag, it\'s exactly what I wanted. Its great quality.','I661706123'),(6,'2014-04-10',5,'Comfortable','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Shorts\', \'Casual\']]','Comfortable shorts to do yoga in. Have no issues with them slipping down as others have mentioned. Wear them to class a couple times a week and couldn\'t be happier.','I330290793'),(7,'2012-05-12',5,'Another Wonderful Shoe from Dansko','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'D\', \'Dansko\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Fashion Sneakers\']]','I ordered these for the balance between looks and comfort and they do not disappoint. Cute enough to be worn with casual summer dresses and skirt they are sturdy enough and comfortable enough to make walking long distances appealing. The same with standing for long periods. There is a reason that so many nurses and doctors wear the standard Dansko Clog.These do look like the little summer sneakers we love to wear around. Dansko quality is also unmatched. I own 2 pairs of clogs and a pair of boots by Dansko, all of which have lasted years and all of which still look well and are comfortable when worn. Worth the investment. I see from some reviews that some people with foot problems don\'t like these. Not every shoe is for everybody. Most people love Dansko, so give their ergonomic foot bed and arch support a try and see if it works with your foot. Highest possible recommendation.','I284382593'),(8,'2013-12-10',5,'Cute Boots','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'U\', \'UGG\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Boots\']]','I chose this rating because I like them. My 18 year old granddaughter has asked for them for Christmas, (she doesn\'t know I have them.) She has worn UGG\'s before, so I know she will love them. As usual, the service from Amazon Prime has been prompt and I love the updates.','I251191438'),(9,'2014-07-09',4,'But I will use them as a good comfortable walking shoes','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'G\', \'Grasshoppers\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Shoes\', \'Athletic\', \'Walking\']]','The shoes fit and soft. But I wish the look is more youthful.They look rather &#34;Granny&#34; . But I will use them as a good comfortable walking shoes.','I437530446'),(10,'2013-12-31',4,'Looks exactly like the photo','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'Blouses & Button-Down Shirts\']]','My shirt arrived today and it looks just like the photo, the photo itself gives off the slight impression that the sleeves look like silk or something similar, this is not true. Just to let you know, the sleeves on the item are cloth and made of a stretchy material. I really like the way it fits, i take a size Large in shirts these days and i ordered an XL just to be safe, it fits well, all in all i am very happy with this purchase. And ordering a size up payed off, the shirt fits perfectly.','I775395395'),(11,'2013-12-05',5,'Great school bag','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'N\', \'Nine West\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Handbags & Wallets\', \'Top-Handle Bags\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Handbags & Wallets\', \'Shoulder Bags\']]','I\'m a graduate student, and I\'ve been using this as my school bag for two quarters & a summer so far! It fits: my Macbook 13&#34; Air in a neoprene case, thin folders, my Kleen Kanteen, wallet, snack, cell phone, lotion, and assorted personal items -- basically, everything I need for a full day of school!This bag can take a lot of weight, and it\'s held up really well. Because of the way the handles are wrapped and the material, it doesn\'t seem like I\'ll need to worry about fraying handles (what killed my other school bags). The only thing is that the black band around the lock fell off after about 6 months of use, but I just chipped the glue off with the edge of a steel ruler, and it looks fine.I recommend it!','I915012432'),(12,'2013-11-01',5,'fit, quality review','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Clothing\', \'Shirts\', \'T-Shirts\']]','Tee shirt is awesome, heavy weight, quality material, true to size: boxy men\'s fit. Clean and simple lines, well made, thick stitching and the absolute best prices on the planet. These are not Hanes or Fruit of the Looms, more like Costco or higher end tee\'s. Buy several. My husband is 6\'4, 200lbs, XL is slightly too large, my friend is 6\', 215 lbs, the xl fits him perfectly.','I065416460'),(13,'2014-05-08',5,'Lots of compliments','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'Blouses & Button-Down Shirts\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Plus-Size\', \'Tops & Tees\', \'Blouses & Button-Down Shirts\']]','When you wear this you get lots and lots of compliments.  It is a beautiful and comfortable shirt. Love the color too','I627533415'),(14,'2014-05-20',5,'VERY GIRLIE!  JUST LIKE MOI!!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Dresses\', \'Casual\']]','The dress is thicker (more layers) than I thought.  Which is just great, I\'m not complaining!  Can\'t wait for MN weather to hurry up and warm up so I can wear the dress!!!','I492708565'),(15,'2014-01-18',5,'Perfect','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Accessories\', \'Hats & Caps\', \'Skullies & Beanies\']]','Exactly what I wanted. Great price, arrived quickly, quality and color are fantastic. Keeps my head nice and wa