alk around in them too much because my heel began to hurt.  If I had not worn them, I would have returned them.','I275097306'),(36,'2014-02-23',4,'LOVE THESE!!!!','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Plus-Size\', \'Jeans\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Novelty\', \'Clothing\', \'Women\', \'Leggings\']]','These are by far my favourite leggings, I just wish the waistband was 100x better. It doesn\'t fit tightly so it sags.','I874288210'),(37,'2014-02-06',4,'PRETTY','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Novelty\', \'Jewelry\', \'Necklaces & Pendants\']]','I LIKE THIS, IT LOOKS VERY VINTAGE. I LIKE THE COLORS AND THE PEACOCK. I HAVEN\'T WORN IT YET, BUT PLAN ON IT.','I003716158'),(38,'2014-04-10',1,'see thru','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Dresses\']]','I can see right thru this. I wasnt a fan of the sleeves either but I did recieve the belt which is pretty cute. Soooo thats cool, right?','I815510638'),(39,'2014-03-06',5,'Merino','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Clothing\', \'Underwear\', \'Thermal Underwear\', \'Tops\']]','I never knew about Merino until my recent trip to New York.  I grew up thinking that all wool products were itchy and uncomfortable.  After wearing Merino, I don\'t think that I could ever go back to the synthetics like BodyArmor and other brands employ.  The Merino kept me warm when out in the freezing temperatures of New York but cool enough to wear indoors with the heater on, too -- Hell, I have worn it on several early morning hikes after returning to Arizona.  Extremely comfortable and doesn\'t pill when washed like another merino shirt that I ordered.','I516546542'),(40,'2013-11-24',5,'Warmth at a good price','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Shoes & Accessories: International Shipping Available\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'E\', \'EMU Australia\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry