othing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Jeans\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Plus-Size\', \'Jeans\']]','Levi\'s are my absolute favorite jeans.  I am thick through the waist, hips and thighs. The 512 and 542 Levi\'s styles are the most comfortable for my shape.  The sizing is unpredictable/inconsistent so if you don\'t have the patience to deal with that inconvenience then you may want to seek a different brand.  For me, no other brand compares.  I ordered 3 pairs of this style in the same size but all different colors.  Two pairs measured 37&#34;-38&#34; in the waist - perfect.  One pair (unscripted) measured 34&#34; in the waist - too small.  Other than the sizing issues, these jeans are very comfortable.  They hug in a way that looks good on a plus size woman.  The back pockets are positioned perfectly. The tummy panel is great with one exception - very shallow front pockets.  I carry nothing important in the front pockets because they are so shallow. That\'s not really an issue for me as don\'t carry things in my pockets anyway.  In the rare need for pockets, the back pockets are my choice. They are boot cut but not too wide as is the case with many other boot cut jeans.  I don\'t like the flare leg look nor do I like the skinny leg look. I simply love these jeans!!Regarding my experience with sizing:Being a repeat Levi\'s customer for 30+ years; I have noticed what seems to be a trend depending on where the jeans were made. First, let me emphasize that when these were made exclusively in the USA, I wore the 550 style and I never encountered erratic sizing issues to the point of &#34;doesn\'t fit at all&#34; that I sometimes encounter now.  As with most clothing brands, they started manufacturing in other countries in order to compete and to stay in business.  When ordered in my normal size:-Made in China runs between too small to perfect sizing.-Made in Pakistan runs between perfect sizing to too large.-I have never received jeans made in China that were too large and I have never received jeans made in Pakistan that were too small.-Made in Pakistan is more often perfect sizing than those Made in China. (In my recent order, 2 pairs from Pakistan fit perfect while one pair from China was too small)OK, I know that may not be very helpful but I wanted to share it because this explains why one reviewer states; these jeans are too small, the next reviewer states; these jeans are too big, and then the next reviewer states; I should have just ordered my normal size.  In my experience I find it is best to just order my normal size because I win more often that way.  Notice that I said more often, not always. It is most probable that hundreds of happy customers order their normal size and simply do not bother to write reviews.','I021185366'),(334,'2013-01-28',3,'Not what I thought I ordered','[[\'Sports & Outdoors\', \'Clothing\', \'Men\', \'Socks\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Clothing\', \'Active\', \'Athletic Socks\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Men\', \'Big & Tall\']]','This is not the product I thought I had ordered.  When these arrived, I was quite surprised and disappointed.However, my Son says they are just fine for socks so that\'s why I gave them three stars.','I331002038'),(335,'2013-07-07',5,'GOOD','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\'], [\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Novelty, Costumes & More\', \'Novelty\', \'Jewelry\', \'Bracelets\']]','THIS ANKLET LOOKS GOOD AND IS EASY TO TAKE OFF AND PUT ON.  I LIKE THIS CLASP THAT THEY USED.','I422257159'),(336,'2013-03-06',5,'very comfortable and pretty','[[\'Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry\', \'Women\', \'Clothing\', \'Dresses\', \'Casual\']]','This dress is a good deal. It is pretty, comfortable, and modest. Its perfect for hot days and warm nights. It is figure flattering, but not if you carry weight in your tummy. I am very pleased with this versatile dress!','I011994385'),(337,'2010-11-14',3,'Comfortable shoes','[[\'